{"type": "article", "id": 2776, "title": "Wavy 茶具", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-11T07:50:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232540cmNzR0VIiSB6KlMW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自香港的工业设计专业学生 Patricia Wong 设计制作了一套名为“ Wavy ”的茶具，用她的话说，这是一套”活着的茶具”，每一款都设计制作了非常有意思的手柄，如花瓣一般层叠张开，采用注浆的方式制作，灵感来源于类似吹制玻璃的手法，从而造就了整套茶具组合的独特外形和感觉，也使得手握的感觉更加自然舒适。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232538eZAmlBjXDLJ8iyR9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325391EiGYPBJkZ36dq0W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232539mSUHn1ZLrIP6XDC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232539pZAS8xfDGtV4QMLY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232540VQPwdIziDpUmx7W1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}